Come party with us this Cinco de Mayo. We have drink specials (tequila, rum and vodka as well as a ton of beers), delicious Mexican inspired appetizers and of course some killer live music lined up. Plus we'll be hosting a mystery giveaway you won't want to miss. So grab a sombrero and get your nalgas over here on Thursday May 5, 2016!

Then leave the keys at home, make some friends on the bus and get  home safe at the end of the night!
